{"blogid": "126675882", "writerAge": "码龄10年", "writerBlogNum": "65", "writerCollect": "117", "writerComment": "14", "writerFan": "14", "writerGrade": "3级", "writerIntegral": "437", "writerName": "Wish3D", "writerProfileAdress": "..\\..\\static\\writer_image\\profile_126675882.jpg", "writerRankTotal": "35422", "writerRankWeekly": "暂无排名", "writerThumb": "27", "writerVisitNum": "57484", "blog_read_count": "258", "blog_time": "于 2022-09-02 17:17:27 发布", "blog_title": "怎样基于VitePress（Vite官网主题）写自己文档", "content": "<div class=\"article_content clearfix\" id=\"article_content\">\n<link href=\"../../static/bootstrap/css/csdnstyle.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<div class=\"htmledit_views\" id=\"content_views\">\n<div>\n<p>最近又要写技术文档了，查看了一下市面上的一些文档生成器，如</p>\n<a class=\"wrap external\" href=\"http://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//docsify.js.org/%23/\">docsify</a>\n<a class=\"wrap external\" href=\"http://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//vuepress.vuejs.org/zh/\">http://vuepress.com/、</a>\n<a class=\"wrap external\" href=\"http://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//vitepress.vuejs.org/\">Vite &amp; Vue Powered Static Site Generator</a>\n<p>综合比较还是比较倾向vitepress，vuepress之前用过界面不是很直接，docsify界面布局也不是很理想。vitepress不叫好看的主题就是vite的官网了。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"></p>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<img alt=\"8716cec4405e1519b565645bcb9b32e0.jpeg\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\8716cec4405e1519b565645bcb9b32e0.jpeg\" width=\"1200\"/>\n</div>\n<p>是不是简洁，还带着一些小清新？</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"></p>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<img alt=\"32bbe2d643a54118a32555dc891af039.jpeg\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\32bbe2d643a54118a32555dc891af039.jpeg\" width=\"1200\"/>\n</div>\n<p>二级标题和三级标题更直接明了。</p>\n<h2><b>所以打算白嫖vite网站了。</b></h2>\n<p><b>1.找到开源地址</b></p>\n<p>地址：<a class=\"external\" href=\"http://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//github.com/vitejs/vite\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span class=\"visible\">github.com/vitejs/vite</span><span class=\"invisible\"></span></a> （英文版实时最新的）</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"></p>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<img alt=\"dac1298cfbed2e3f9c1dac22d30952a1.jpeg\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\dac1298cfbed2e3f9c1dac22d30952a1.jpeg\" width=\"973\"/>\n</div>\n<p>地址：<a class=\"external\" href=\"http://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//github.com/vitejs/docs-cn\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span class=\"visible\">github.com/vitejs/docs-</span><span class=\"invisible\">cn</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a> （中文版有有时间延迟）</p>\n<h2><b>2.git pull代码</b></h2>\n<h2><b>3.修改里面额MD文档形成自己的</b></h2>\n<h2><b>4.怎样杜绝原有赞助广告？</b></h2>\n<p>查看network,可以查看到对应的广告文件请求</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"></p>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<img alt=\"434409c833dac9cdd2193f6195f23903.jpeg\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\434409c833dac9cdd2193f6195f23903.jpeg\" width=\"1067\"/>\n</div>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"></p>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<img alt=\"5ee8587f6e0d78d705e9fed5a433ffbf.png\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\5ee8587f6e0d78d705e9fed5a433ffbf.png\" width=\"680\"/>\n</div>\n<p>上面的json就是对应的广告数据</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"></p>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<img alt=\"382790928338b00707e3ab705d904443.jpeg\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\382790928338b00707e3ab705d904443.jpeg\" width=\"1200\"/>\n</div>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"></p>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<img alt=\"69de6bd12ae884c31922f0c314fb8484.jpeg\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\69de6bd12ae884c31922f0c314fb8484.jpeg\" width=\"1200\"/>\n</div>\n<p>找到对应文件，请求去掉，注释data</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"></p>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<img alt=\"c6156361a421a8e789a81208bdbaf57f.png\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\c6156361a421a8e789a81208bdbaf57f.png\" width=\"678\"/>\n</div>\n<h2><b>5.全文搜索</b></h2>\n<p><b>此处的搜索是用的algolia的docsearch组件，需要</b>algolia注册账号，并获取对应的key，创建database，和index </p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"></p>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<img alt=\"3bcf9667b96900a03e73b7733dd5e9d8.png\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\3bcf9667b96900a03e73b7733dd5e9d8.png\" width=\"937\"/>\n</div>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"></p>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<img alt=\"6a9714805b5d9ef40923bc62746ae818.jpeg\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\6a9714805b5d9ef40923bc62746ae818.jpeg\" width=\"1142\"/>\n</div>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"></p>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<img alt=\"1bd7f48fb46425c2fdc934eac6b3bb3d.jpeg\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\1bd7f48fb46425c2fdc934eac6b3bb3d.jpeg\" width=\"1015\"/>\n</div>\n<p>这样你就拥有一个md文档生成器了</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>", "first_tag": "Others", "cpp": 0, "csharp": 0, "python": 0, "javascript": 0, "java": 0, "sql": 0, "php": 0, "time": "2022-09-02 17:17:27", "summary": "最近又要写技术文档了，查看了一下市面上的一些文档生成器，如、综合比较还是比较倾向，之前用过界面不是很直接，界面布局也不是很理想。不叫好看的主题就是的官网了。是不是简洁，还带着一些小清新？二级标题和三级"}